    <item>
      <title>特朗普称 Meta 的扎克伯格最近经常给他打电话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/trump-says-meta-s-zuckerberg-has-been-calling-him-a-lot-lately</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，Meta Platforms Inc. 首席执行官马克·扎克伯格在过去几周多次给他打电话，包括在 7 月中旬这位前美国总统面临暗杀企图之后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/trump-says-meta-s-zuckerberg-has-been-calling-him-a-lot-lately</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 19:34:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗获得选举委员会批准，争取胜利合法化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/maduro-gets-electoral-council-nod-in-bid-to-legitimize-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉选举机构批准了总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗的胜利，最高法院开始对选举结果进行听证，马杜罗政府试图利用政权控制的机构来使其地位合法化，以应对欺诈指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/maduro-gets-electoral-council-nod-in-bid-to-legitimize-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 19:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥熊队老板迈克尔·萨克斯 (Michael Sacks) 建议普利兹克担任哈里斯副总裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/michael-sacks-chicago-bears-owner-make-pitch-for-pritzker-as-harris-vp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊利诺伊州企业高管和民主党捐助大佬们正在敦促副总统卡马拉·哈里斯选择州长 JB 普利兹克作为她的竞选伙伴，并指出普利兹克在吸引商业活动到该州方面取得了成就。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/michael-sacks-chicago-bears-owner-make-pitch-for-pritzker-as-harris-vp</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 18:50:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普 2020 年案件在豁免裁决后被发回下级法院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/trump-2020-case-sent-back-to-lower-court-after-immunity-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院上个月裁定总统享有广泛的起诉豁免权，周五正式将针对唐纳德·特朗普干预选举的联邦刑事案件发回华盛顿的一名法官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/trump-2020-case-sent-back-to-lower-court-after-immunity-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:59:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗报复性打击迫在眉睫，以色列与美国、英国合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/israel-working-with-us-uk-as-retaliatory-strike-from-iran-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防官员表示，他们正在与美国和英国在伊朗预计的袭击之前进行协调，为重复今年 4 月伊朗发动的类似袭击做好准备，当时伊朗的盟友击退了袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/israel-working-with-us-uk-as-retaliatory-strike-from-iran-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国司法部加大力度避免选举混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-justice-department-steps-up-efforts-to-avoid-election-mayhem</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部正在为 11 月的总统大选做准备，该部正在关注投票权斗争、调查威胁，并准备恢复与社交媒体公司的简报，以遏制错误信息的传播。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-justice-department-steps-up-efforts-to-avoid-election-mayhem</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么俄罗斯人参加奥运会，而俄罗斯人却不参加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/why-russia-belarus-aren-t-competing-at-paris-olympics-but-their-athletes-are</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯的传统体育实力使得其国歌成为现代奥运会颁奖仪式上的常规旋律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/why-russia-belarus-aren-t-competing-at-paris-olympics-but-their-athletes-are</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
